      "description": "The FT Vest U.S. Equity Quarterly 2.5 to 15 Buffer ETF (DHDG) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in downside hedge alternatives. The fund aims to participate in the price movement of the SPDR S&P 500 ETF (ticker: SPY), up to a cap while buffering losses between -2.5% and -15%. The fund resets its buffer and cap levels quarterly DHDG was launched on Nov 3, 2016 and is issued by First Trust.",
